Import a Decision.

   Import Decision configuration from an export file.

  Example:
  ```
  mutation {
  importDecision (
    input: {
      info: "There can be only one true pizza. Choose wisely."
      jsonData: " {
        "decision" => ...
      }
      "
      keywords: [
        a,b,12
      ]
      language: "en"
      slug: "pizza-chooser"
      title: "Pizza Chooser Extraordinaire"
    }
  ) {
    id
  }
}
  ```
  returns

  ```
  {
  "data": {
    "importDecision": {
      "id": 300
    }
  }
}
  ```

